{"tid":2016583,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)無聲火 驚天奪寶1-2","createTime":"2020-05-14T13:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T19:18:32.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"234e59ee3bf44f692707e9d3f70ac15f612f952c","tid":2016583,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:15:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7sbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=75516410\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7sbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=e36e2989\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7sbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=8e553214\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d7/Bangkok_Dangerous_poster_%282008_American_film_Version%29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd7%2FBangkok_Dangerous_poster_%25282008_American_film_Version%2529.jpg&h=ed7ee382&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/38/National_treasure.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F38%2FNational_treasure.jpg&h=5617bdf9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/90/National_treasure_book_of_secrets.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F90%2FNational_treasure_book_of_secrets.jpg&h=62425bc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.喬（尼可拉斯&middot;凱吉飾）原本是個冷血職業殺手，但即將發生意想不到的轉變，一切都要從泰國曼谷說起&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n喬原本前往泰國是要執行任務，他僱用一個街頭混混來幫忙毀滅他殺人的證據。但奇怪的是，一向獨來獨往的他，卻發現和那個街頭混混開始交心。而且還被一個女店員深深吸引了，這讓他覺得他要不要繼續當殺手<br />\n<br />\n2.傳說三千多年前，古埃及時代流傳下來一筆逐漸累積的巨額寶藏，直到美國開國之初，這筆寶藏成了當時美國建國者們的「國安基金」，但是經過兩百多年的時空演變，這筆寶藏下落已經不明。而蓋茲一家相傳在美國開國之初，就被授與保護這筆「國家寶藏」的任務。班傑明&middot;富蘭克林&middot;蓋茲是一個喜愛考古的冒險家，他從小在爺爺的灌輸之下，堅信國家寶藏的存在。班傑明和負責金援的英國人伊恩進行寶藏的追查，他們在冰天雪地的北極中找到了一艘古船。班傑明在這艘古船上找到一隻菸斗，進而發現線索藏在美國開國的文章&mdash;&mdash;「獨立宣言」的背面...<br />\n<br />\n3.美國內戰結束五天之後，約翰&middot;威爾克斯&middot;布思（John Wilkes Booth）和另一個人拿著一本日記去找湯瑪斯&middot;蓋茲（班&middot;蓋茲的高祖父）日記裡含有一段被加密的信息，托馬斯認出了加密方式，並開始解密。此時布思離開客棧前往福特劇院去刺殺林肯。托馬斯發現日記記載的是一處寶藏，並識破了布思等南方同盟企圖盜取寶藏的陰謀。他撕下那頁日記投入壁爐，被同行者搶救出的只是殘頁，而他也被同行者射殺。垂死的托馬斯告訴兒子查爾斯：「The debt that all men pay」<br />\n<br />\n10 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7sbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=9080291c\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7sbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=26b953a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9cde4a15dd3b94f5b7cb78c64a825b1126459cd","tid":2016583,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e9d0a55407bb04b7331e0f9017d62d1b429ec3","tid":2016583,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T14:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d00f970491a789ed3d0d0823d78040ab0145702","tid":2016583,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T15:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a6b941430207e1973120d3a7e9507b9e94559f","tid":2016583,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T16:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ded9fac6fb7368cc20a97ab1323d16c21421313","tid":2016583,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T19:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}